{"tid":1560471,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"法官: 現時證據並非律政司所指的「強而有力」","createTime":"2019-09-11T08:06:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T08:36:34.000Z","uid":40667,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"9a9e255fc507027f5f0b031b784a26001adef252","tid":1560471,"uid":40667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T08:06:47.000Z","msg":"涉向警署擲石20歲女學生准以20萬元保釋到波蘭進修<br />\n<br />\n一批示威者上月29日在深水埗警署外集結，以鐳射筆照射警署內的警員，有5人涉嫌擲石頭入警署。其中被捕的一名20歲女學生被控暴動罪，九龍城裁判法院署理主任裁判官嚴舜儀早前批准她保釋外出，但拒絕離港交流的申請。高等法院法官邱智立今日考慮現有證據後，批准被告於今年9月至明年2月到波蘭留學進修，亦批准她毋須出席11月11日的聆訊。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">法官觀看律政司提供的有關片段後，認為現時證據並非律政司所指的「強而有力」</span></span>，又表示進修是鼓勵青年人所做的行為，因此批准被告更改保釋條件申請，以20萬現金保釋外出，獲准在一段時間內離港到波蘭進修。另外，在港時需遵守晚上10時至早上6時的宵禁令，定時到馬鞍山警署報道，需居住於申報地址等。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1480006-20190911.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1480006-20190911.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=33lQL0pOg%2F%2Bbj%2F%2FH3PrIWe2wegjmRFMzjbv%2B285MJ7g%3D&h=6e434944\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1480006-20190911.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=d192d154\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1480006-20190911.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9f894321bebba4bff51269aefdc5f4b4fe05642","tid":1560471,"uid":146737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T08:07:38.000Z","msg":"針對中立淺藍黃嘅文宣【牆紙！】<br />\n<br />\n第四期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1547783/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1547783/page/1</a><br />\n第三期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.co